A ripped out journal page
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Don't think,


For they will think for you


One thousand thoughts.



P.S. God forgive me for what I've done.


Why have I written this? Why have I killed them? I -- Alessandro Faraday -- a murderer!


It's them. The voices. The whispers. They forced my mind... my hand... They made me do it!


What's going on here? Why am I drawn to this red pillar? Why is it calling to me?


I will find out.